data.description: Welcome to your stunning home in highly sought after Ocean View! Get ready to entertain in the extensive and fully fenced backyard with its impressive deck, hot tub, patio, and gorgeous stone fire pit. HVAC is less than 3 years old with a 10-year warranty. The following are brand new: crown molding throughout home, reverse osmosis system, garage door opener, water softener, ceiling fans in the bedrooms, and front door entrance keypad. Enjoy the best of beach living with 2 separate beach entrances within one block of home, kayak/paddle board launch at 10 Bay Street, OV Fishing Pier, and East Ocean View Rec Center with its fishing pier and kayak launch. Family fun continues with the seasonal Farmers Market, Bay Oaks Park, and incredible dining at several of Hampton Roads’ award winning restaurants. This golf cart friendly community has a blast coasting among the area’s best breweries. Located between JEB Little Creek and Norfolk Naval Bases, this home offers everything you can dream of.
